* {{ill|Bunsei (era)|ja|文政|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  5 (Gregorian {{ill|1822|ja|1822nd year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|May 11|ja|5月11日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Kurikoma Jōun|ja|栗本鋤雲|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|bakufu|ja|幕臣|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  official and {{ill|journalist|ja|ジャーナリスト|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  (+ {{ill|1897|ja|1897th year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ).

* {{ill|Kaei (era)|ja|嘉永|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  1 (Gregorian {{ill|1848|ja|1848th year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|April 13|ja|4月13日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Asano Sōichirō|ja|浅野総一郎|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} , entrepreneur and founder of the {{ill|Asano zaibatsu|ja|浅野財閥|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  (+ {{ill|1930|ja|1930th year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ).

* {{ill|Keiō (era)|ja|慶応|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  2 (Gregorian {{ill|1866|ja|1866th year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|April 24|ja|4月24日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Ishii Kikujirō|ja|石井菊次郎|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} , Japanese {{ill|diplomat|ja|外交官|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  (+ {{ill|1945|ja|1945th year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ).

* {{ill|Meiji (era)|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  4 (Gregorian {{ill|1871|ja|1871st year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|April 29|ja|4月29日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Yoshioka Yayoi|ja|吉岡弥生|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} , physician and founder of {{ill|Tokyo Women's Medical University|ja|東京女子医科大学|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  (+ {{ill|1959|ja|1959th year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ).

== Deaths ==

* Emperor Monmu 4 (Julian {{ill|700|ja|700th year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|April 3|ja|4月3日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Dōshō|ja|道昭|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} , Buddhist monk.

* {{ill|Enryaku (era)|ja|延暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  9 (Intercalary March) (Julian {{ill|790|ja|790th year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|April 28|ja|4月28日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Fujiwara no Otomuro|ja|藤原乙牟漏|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} , Empress of {{ill|Emperor Kanmu|ja|桓武天皇|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  (* {{ill|760|ja|760th year|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ).

